      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a strong start, but it's a bit too generic. I need it to really hit home on the specific threats we're seeing. Can you lean harder into the idea that these progressive \"redefinitions\" of gender and family aren't just different opinions, but are actually dangerous to the stability of our kids and the future of the country? Make it feel like a moral necessity to fight back.",
